g.text: It’s a waste of money to stay in hospital and to do so many useless examination and treatment. I can recover by myself.
“We need to be medical workers as well as servers, we can’t face everyone with smile for we are too busy”

I like to workout and have a healthy body, but this time I felt abdomen pain, and came to the hospital. The doctor said that I need a operation, without explanation. After that I have to do many treatment and pay much money. The tube in my stomach makes me fell embarass, because disgusting liquid flow to everywhere. Other people cannot bear me including the nurse. But I can only let it go, scince I don’t want to trouble my children to help me.

I am the archiater, in charge of dozens of patients. I make usual rounds only once per week. Detailed works are charged by young doctors. But Patients don’t trust them, and they like to talk to me directly. I never refuse them even though I am busy. But patients don’t understand us. They complain about our attitude and never trust us. Communication is realy difficult because they don’t have professional knowledges. The doctor-patient relation-ship is rather tense.
